highlights.text: “Black Out Days (Stay Away)” by Ian Asher and Phantogram is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Hong Kong at #94.
TENBLANK has the most spots on Viral Songs Hong Kong. “旋律と結晶” is the highest at #15.
“零距离的思念” by TINY 7 has been on Viral Songs Hong Kong the longest, at 155 days straight.
“Glass Heart” by TENBLANK is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Hong Kong, up 20 spots at #48.
